2009: Began his professional career on the European Challenge Tour. Made nine starts, playing on the weekend in six of those events. Best finish was a T16 at the SK Golf Challenge in early August, a final-round 69 leaving him tied with two others, six shots behind winner Nicolas Colsaerts.

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the PGA TOUR was T39th in 2015 at the CIMB Classic.
